  - profile: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c3ddfbe6bf7e1994890e6d9377883188, type: 2}
    introText: "And this is Svadhisthana.\nShe is smaller than the others, but that
      is exactly where her strength lies. She can reach places no one else can. Like
      water, she does not fight obstacles \u2014 she simply finds another way through."
